
1) NOTE --> agar kisi method ko abstract declare kiya hai to class ko bhi karna padega.
2) Abstract class contains abstract as well as concrete methods also.
3) We cannot create object for abstract class, but constructor bana sakte hai and use protected declare karna hoga for some reason
4) Agar abstract class ko public nahi kiya to other packages ke child class access nahi kar
   paaenge. Then it will become package private.
5) protected access modifier ke liye inheritance karna jaruri hai